<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 17 at 9:31PM EST  by NWS Raleigh</headline>
<description>...Black ice expected through Tuesday morning...
Temperatures will fall into the 20s overnight and remain there
through mid-morning Tuesday. Areas of black ice can be expected as
any melt water refreezes.
Black ice is difficult to see. Use caution while walking and
traveling.</description>
